  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and saut\u00109 over until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the fennel bulb and cook for an additional 5 minutes, or until slightly tender.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the bonito flakes and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly, until fragrant.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a large baking dish or clay pot with a steamer basket.",
    "Add the chopped parsley and serve over the banana leaves with lemon wedges on the side.",
    "To serve, slice the banana leaves in half and spoon the tagine onto the center of each half.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
